INSERT INTO `love_letter` VALUES ('1200000000001010050', 'partner', 'partner', 'I like you, still the same. May you be happy every day.So, I might learn to put it down and let it go.It wasn\'t what I wanted, and I never thought it would be like this. It\'s my fault. I might not have bothered you, and I shouldn\'t have broken it.Li Jia xin, I like you, but I didn\'t want to embarrass you, and I didn\'t think it would make the relationship between us so awkward, or, as it is, become like a stranger.I just want to say that I like you, no other purpose, just like you, that\'s all.But obviously you don\'t like it, or it interferes with your life.So, I want to say sorry to you. I didn\'t mean to. I want to be with you, but this is obviously not realistic. Because it\'s just that I like you, and it\'s possible to have someone you like, but that person isn\'t me.', '120000000000101', '2b74c61d2ce0e87923220234f3619b7d');
